    "body": "inside `eth_estimageGas` there is a binary search for gas, and it starts with the block's gas limit\r\nthis is where 3 ETH comes from (15m multipled by the gas price of the tx)\r\nso the solution is to disable this check in the context of `eth_estimageGas`",
